Package com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.entity

Class SessionEntity

java.lang.Object
com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.entity.SessionEntity
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Entity public class SessionEntity extends Object implements Serializable
The SessionEntity class represents the "session" table in the database. Each instance of this class corresponds to a single row in the table.
